Media personality Lamiez Holworthy-Morule and her siblings have gifted their mother, Imelda Klow, with a brand new set of wheels for her birthday. Writing on social media, Lamiez said Klow celebrated her birthday at the weekend. Klow, who is also Lamiez’s manager, was surprised when her children revealed the surprise gift. “The matriarch leader of our tribe, thank you for all that you do for us, for all the sacrifices and all the teachings. My greatest gift that I get from her? Her heart. Anyone whose been fortunate enough to experience her can attest to it,” wrote Lamiez.   For the latest entertainment news from Sunday World, click here. Or read the latest from Shwashwi here. Follow @SundayWorldZA on Twitter and @sundayworldza on Instagram, or like our Facebook Page, Sunday World, by clicking here for the latest breaking news in South Africa. To Subscribe to Sunday World, click here.